      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example of the legendary S54-powered coupe. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features a fully serviced VANOS system and updated rod bearings, ensuring peak volumetric efficiency across the 8,000 RPM powerband. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a Variable M Differential Lock. The chassis is impeccable, featuring documented rear subframe reinforcement and a suspension refresh utilizing OEM bushings and Bilstein dampers for period-correct handling. Finished in factory-original paint with zero oxidation and a pristine undercarriage, this vehicle retains its original factory tolerances and mechanical integrity. A true turnkey investment for the discerning purist seeking a benchmark-level driving experience.",
